COMBAT SYSTEM

100% hit chance
10% chance to crit
10% chance to do half damage

Defense = Damage Reduction

------------------------------------------

GAME SETUP
Spawn map => Clone the map so it can't be altered outside of the game and so that we can alter it inside the game!
Players start with a certain number of resources
No units

ON YOUR TURN
Get income for every base (this includes your HQs and any neutral bases you have units on)
Can spend money to purchase units => New units can't move/attack on their first turn.
	-> Can only deploy to the first 3 columns on your side?
Move units
Do attacks

